# Scholarships Plus - Development Notes

## Port Configuration

**IMPORTANT: This app MUST run on port 3030 only.**

Port 3030 is the only port authorized for Google OAuth callbacks.

### Configuration
- Main app: `http://localhost:3030`
- Metrics: `http://localhost:3010/metrics` (internal, for monitoring)
- Remix dev server: Uses automatic port selection for WebSocket/HMR

### Environment Variables
```bash
PORT=3030  # Main app port (set in package.json dev:remix script)
```

### Google OAuth Redirect URI
```
http://localhost:3030/auth/google/callback
```

This is configured in `.env`:
```
GOOGLE_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URI="http://localhost:3030/auth/google/callback"
```

